description:
The top-rated NinJump Deluxe app is now free! Fans of the classic NinJump game will enjoy all-new worlds, conquer new enemies & climb their way to the top with this awesome sequel to the mega-hit NinJump game. 

*** REVIEWS ***

"It's a fast-paced game with great graphics and that all-important 'just one more time' factor." ~ 148Apps.com

"This is a retro treat that once started will prove pretty tricky to put down." ~ Pocket Arcade

"It is a casual, quick, pick-up-and-play title." AppModo.com

*** DESCRIPTION ***

NinJump games have been downloaded over 50 million times by fans around the world. NinJump Deluxe Free includes the same addictive ninja climbing fun in entirely new, heart-pounding settings. Jump your way past sea monsters, witch doctors, tropical snakes, monkeys, fire-breathing dragons and enemy ninjas. Collect shields and amazing new power-ups along the way. Your goal is to jump your way to the top of your screen while avoiding increasingly treacherous obstacles and enemies. How far can you get?

NinJump Deluxe Free comes fully-loaded with:

- New Pirate, Jungle & Castle levels
- Simple, fun single-tap gameplay
- Sea Monsters, Ogres, Dragons & more
- Awesome power-ups & shields
- Leader boards & score sharing
- Amazing graphics & characters

Install NinJump Deluxe Free today


_____________________________________

NinJump Deluxe Free is brought to you by Backflip Studios, makers of absurdly fun mobile games like Paper Toss, DragonVale, Strike Knight, Shape Shift, Army of Darkness Defense, Ragdoll Blaster and Graffiti Ball. Search the App Store for "Backflip Studios" to see all our apps.

Follow @BackflipStudios on Twitter for free game announcements and other updates.

Thanks for playing!
